thread.title_full: Chicago Airbrush Supply reviewed by Richie

author: Richie
title: Richie
text: They have no stock - they ship directly from the manufacturer. The website says 1-5 days, but I finally got my tracking number and it does not deliver until next week - 3 weeks from ordering. Do yourself a favor and get form Amazon - you will get the item in 2 days if you have Prime.
